<node id="DIVIDEND DISTRIBUTION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Dividend distribution is the process by which companies distribute a portion of their profits to shareholders as part of their financial strategy. This process impacts shareholder equity and cash flows. In January 2021, Acme Government Solutions distributed $5 million in dividends to its shareholders, enhancing shareholder returns. MediaCorp also engaged in dividend distribution, with shares based on the company's financial performance in the fiscal year, while Energex similarly distributed dividends to its shareholders symbolizing commitment to providing returns to investors. JetWing Aviation distributed $10 million in dividends to its shareholders in August 2021 and Innovate Tech Solutions distributed $5 million in December 2017. The distribution of profits to shareholders has been a consistent practice for companies like MediaCorp, which distributed $10 million in September and Acme Government Services distributing $5 million in December 2020. The company also declared a dividend distribution of $0.50 per share totaling $20 million in July 2017. In terms of equity, the payment of dividends reduces it as these funds are allocated to shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98ae50a357e908c06836342636d206f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a238ff5c2448b41d18fa44957345522&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03b4693d32773aeec086cc7402c41727&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1fb3002c8cf9fa90de3c4486594fbbf8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-682bb4129b49deaa4acebc62f83a8e88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6dbb472e74bc873af71d8d65bcf6ceee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-090174c2cb7bf04194fe8e9a62df4087&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10805c10ca8626024a2f75fa9445bd1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41c838a1a55426a899002566fd98a6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf23e8c9afaeb305078057509da903a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c75d7d6ea1a5ea53f1a7f73df042e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca9cc985f9b328109771d850ddb9d7cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-936b579b8ed0e019ea6c11e989bc4a86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b59f304ada4f6fddff18261a513d556c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a52c29b443adb1eff8518c6ac7b2290e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad0fc8f1d75b20553c32969a92a1d4cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c4f95e3b67efa5a01d44138f92eafba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9cbd36deea6666d33256e4168c0404e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9027e20e2ca529838140cc0d50ce0e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5dcdee98fb35a40a6d5df48cfb39eae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01c8196a69aea1f848381063465d0b92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea3aefbaaa32cd145ff0996edc3f3157&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86068dde10a230e2e4323fb0cac9f2a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4275361b1ff0e0dc83b5b680509ff055&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37cc52e260d6db9c2ec026cb15d9cfd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05b1df56df1d4942de8cd7a4a008f08a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92f61129d650c902821daae74f036cc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd5dde358500088ff752a3a847348b82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccd20b38d319fcb10c949517af3c1712&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72f5f3c95233a71f9587b49bf45bccc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9b1776dfe60fdf108bd10ef01d34bf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2458dee186e2f83729a72926b2669800&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3927aec3454fc165bbf6552d5dcdf989&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b97ee95334354a8f34b08d8e478a88ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7243c82f61473ea7124d64666c8a35cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bad1b365c7cc5db04a8ec547800c107b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1925cc8dbf576c0efbb71978f3c6bb3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1595bc63912d3131553c638d8afb11d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d3080d8490190ea1e4344239d03f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5c9692bc747d74650bef3f518902751&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22b7ef362c3a11fd3