<node id="GOVERNMENT CONTRACT ACQUISITION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Acme Government Solutions successfully acquired a major government contract worth $100 million in March 2021, expanding service portfolio and increasing revenue potential.&lt;SEP&gt;Acme's successful acquisition of a major government contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Acquisition of a major government contract worth $100 million in March 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2021, Acme Government Solutions acquired a major government contract worth $100 million.&lt;SEP&gt;The acquisition of a major government contract by Acme in March 2021.</data>
