<node id="$5 MILLION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">The amount by which EduCorp's liabilities were reduced during debt restructuring.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount by which liabilities were reduced through the refinancing process during debt restructuring in August 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount distributed as dividends by Acme Government Solutions in January 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed by Culture Innovators Ltd. in October 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed to shareholders by Acme Government Services in January 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed to shareholders by Acme Government Solutions in January 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed to shareholders by Retail Emporium in 2020, enhancing shareholder returns.</data>
