<node id="ASSET ACQUISITION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Acme Government Solutions completed the acquisition of Nationwide Security Services in February 2021 for a total value of $20 million.&lt;SEP&gt;Acquisition of assets by InnovateTech Solutions, possibly to enhance its operations or capabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Acquisition of assets increases total assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Buildcorp Holdings acquired additional assets, potentially for strategic expansion or value enhancement.&lt;SEP&gt;MediaCorp made significant asset acquisitions in 2018.&lt;SEP&gt;Process of acquiring assets, contributing to total assets value.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchases of additional assets by Buildcorp Holdings aimed at expanding its operational capabilities or portfolio value.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchases or acquisitions adding to the company's asset base.&lt;SEP&gt;The acquisition of Global Education Solutions represents a significant asset acquisition for EduCorp.&lt;SEP&gt;The acquisition of Greenfield Cosmetics by Hudson Consumer Goods Co., which involved purchasing assets for strategic expansion.&lt;SEP&gt;The acquisition of MedTech Innovations for $50 million expanded HealthLife Solutions' business scope.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of acquiring additional assets to increase Stellar Entertainment's total asset value.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of acquiring new assets for HealthLife Solutions, which contributes to total assets.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of acquiring new assets for a business.&lt;SEP&gt;Vanguard Media Group acquired assets during 2019, contributing to its growth strategy.</data>
