<node id="DEBT RATIO">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt Ratio is a crucial financial metric that reflects a company's debt level in relation to its assets and overall financial health. Across various entities such as Energen Solutions Ltd, GreenTech Solutions Inc., JetWing Aviation, Elevate Retail Inc., HealthLife Solutions, Artistic Creations Inc., Hudson Consumer Goods Co., MediaCorp, and Retail Emporium, the Debt Ratio values range from 25% to 59%. These figures indicate a diverse level of debt across these entities. For instance, Energen Solutions Ltd's Debt Ratio is at 34.78%, GreenTech Solutions Inc.'s at 30%, JetWing Aviation's at 40%, and Elevate Retail Inc.'s at 40%. On the other hand, HealthLife Solutions shows a higher ratio of 59% reflecting its financial leverage level. Artistic Creations Inc., after restructuring, saw a decrease in Debt Ratio to 0.47, indicating improved financial stability. Hudson Consumer Goods Co. maintains a balanced Debt Ratio of 0.5, showing that half of the company's assets are financed by debt. MediaCorp and Retail Emporium have relatively low Debt Ratios at 25% and 70%, respectively, suggesting their healthy financial positions compared to total assets. EduCorp, with its ratio standing at 53%, reflects a balanced leverage position, while others like GreenTech Solutions Inc. demonstrate proactive measures in managing debt levels. Overall, the Debt Ratio provides insights into each company's ability to manage debt effectively and sustain long-term financial stability.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6c51db901e8861688472a88b13059f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-337f69c70d0d25eb1377f55716d42ef7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc1bc3addf48e43605fb025cbfd7f231&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ec53492910bb963ddbbbc579f0fd3b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d5b9a6230849cbd0ceb12bdacc8d930&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29b04373f51800d63eea38f5969cf0b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-16c76249e8721e8b155325af6faf1953&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2c6668c781612bc4cfed9959b3a72af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33eefa87cd653a0902ad8bb24f4ee9ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18caea3ff0aef95985c460898a0bec16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9b4e92c1b427ceedb92447393d4d6b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc4e73e01fc6be1f2a3a65b213b59c8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83e808b8711f18dda66b0fc1c4ad9351&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bcc5a8cecdc12ef01423a16041e7f731&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aed2d109c9525bda21552db168fc971d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-295d0141abde05a4719f3b383d07c788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1985fe44245a74e561ef855d9b45c59c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f76e6f51915ca0ca4e1fa04d61ed412d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2add3db4f644e304d4288964b61b2a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc3208201d6561b422fb226e4ff25a4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8b40db867940937f296fa9a6683ef26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f78bff1213a8aeb18c49a9150ee8390&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68ab7d5ce1623cc04843c92af4bded19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7464e6549bfd33747c77ecb5cb886c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc998caae59f4c4aed5f7b3ee1a7ef66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac24a72c7e4b25443159dc621feeb211&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b66c40857191417b60e60f565f026a50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c12f88190379568a6f245f9e2d8a9369&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-574b9a5209d426ecc05b332c4f3cb54e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-affa74002724dde27455d0cbc1953370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ca9523bd7f6636f9a9ba3b9957651f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f8cc7afd0b4444e4c603aa97c816151&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d3080d8490190ea1e4344239d03f12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3feddd6ebe8f5225d8068101fb9790fb</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 50}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 278}]</data>
