<node id="RETURN ON EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Return on Equity (ROE) is a financial ratio that measures a company's profitability by revealing how much profit it generates with the money shareholders have invested, calculated as net income divided by shareholders' equity. A return on equity of 10% reflects consistent growth in net profit and effective utilization of shareholder equity, indicating efficient use of shareholder investments to generate profits. The ROE serves as a measure of financial performance, operational efficiency, and profitability relative to shareholders' equity, demonstrating the company's ability to generate returns for its investors based on their invested capital. Examples include InnovaTech with a 23% ROE, JetWing Aviation at 18%, Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services at 14.5%, and others such as Elevate Retail Inc. at 5.52%, each reflecting the operational efficiency of shareholder equity in generating profits.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6c51db901e8861688472a88b13059f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6af4c1ac610ec6d3ef21911a49d8aaba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98ae50a357e908c06836342636d206f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4c8f45cb1304b97e112f330c9db56a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2c6668c781612bc4cfed9959b3a72af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf4f858d4b518728fad074c21fe34c01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0396f321b40762e78e7ee6efabe134d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18caea3ff0aef95985c460898a0bec16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40eb83ff0e96f6ef7a778941a9956361&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93d9d20a22ca740891c5b696f26e1d02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aed2d109c9525bda21552db168fc971d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1350447933b30bb47a239465034199dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-295d0141abde05a4719f3b383d07c788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a755f31a89c0b0f4817758389cb1c71a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afacf702fc6cb863996a2752adbb999b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe8b781f5104d8951c214db986673a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68ab7d5ce1623cc04843c92af4bded19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f691aff1904a5b36b6c07ec8ca762a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8199cc796723aac9047ec54e229d202a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bb55e357468d99a5a9211bf39eaec21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd67a77a05f79ec6b1ae63875f1533e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43321794b440f22a3185e50b3242b68&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac24a72c7e4b25443159dc621feeb211&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b66c40857191417b60e60f565f026a50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-635dd634ef004a57e780cede9f63dab2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11493ee1e077bc69eb110a807eb081c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-574b9a5209d426ecc05b332c4f3cb54e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ca9523bd7f6636f9a9ba3b9957651f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adf4f37023cc9a29ca9b4647b5a4c1a8</data>
