<node id="NEW CEO">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">A new CEO with extensive experience in the IT industry was appointed to lead the company in March 2017, signaling a potential shift in strategic direction.&lt;SEP&gt;A new CEO with extensive expertise in renewable energy was appointed to lead Energen Solutions Ltd, boosting investor confidence and improving strategic decision-making.&lt;SEP&gt;A new individual appointed as the CEO of the company in October 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual appointed as the new CEO of Elevate Retail following the change in senior management.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual responsible for bringing fresh leadership and expertise to MediaCorp.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO appointed in January 2019 was responsible for driving the company's growth strategy.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO appointed in May 2019 brought significant changes to Sunrise Holidays, focusing on adapting to market dynamics and seizing growth opportunities.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO brought extensive experience in the organic agriculture industry, providing fresh leadership to drive strategic initiatives and enhance the company's competitive position.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO has been appointed to guide Sunrise Holidays, leading to innovative strategies for customer satisfaction and operational efficiency.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO led the company with a strategic vision that contributed significantly to its growth and market competitiveness.&lt;SEP&gt;The new CEO was hired in April 2017 to bring fresh leadership and expertise to the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The newly appointed CEO played a crucial role in shaping the company's strategy and decision-making processes.</data>
