  <data key="d1">Los Angeles is a major city located in California, USA. It serves as a hub for various industries including media and entertainment.&lt;SEP&gt;Los Angeles is a major city located in California, United States. It serves as the cultural and entertainment hub for Stellar Entertainment Holdings Ltd.&lt;SEP&gt;Los Angeles is a major city located in California, known for its entertainment industry.</data>
