<node id="$50 MILLION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">EcoGuard Solutions raised $50 million through equity and debt financing in April 2019, enhancing its financial capacity for expansion.&lt;SEP&gt;Entertainment Enterprises Inc. invested $50 million in the production of The Great Escape.&lt;SEP&gt;In January 2017, Evergreen Consumer Goods Co. distributed $50 million of dividends to its shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount distributed in dividends to shareholders by Stellar Entertainment in March 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of capital raised by InnovateTech to support its expansion and development initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of dividends distributed by SkyQuest in July.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of funds raised by Artistic Creations Inc. during its financing activity in July.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of funds raised by EduCorp from private investors and institutional lenders.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of funds raised by InnovaTech from venture capital firms and strategic investors.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of funds raised by InnovateTech Solutions during the large-scale financing activity in March 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of funds raised through bond issuance by Elevate Retail Inc. in October 2020.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of investment made into Project Green Harvest in March 2018.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount of liability reduction achieved through the debt restructuring strategy in January 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The company generated a cash flow of $50 million from its operating, investment, and financing activities.&lt;SEP&gt;The net profit achieved by HealthLife Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The net profit for JetWing Aviation was $50 million, indicating strong earnings within a certain accounting period.&lt;SEP&gt;The reduction in liabilities resulting from debt restructuring.&lt;SEP&gt;The significant investment amount allocated by GreenTech Solutions Inc. for Project CleanAir in September 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The significant investment made by Capital Finance Group in Project Delta in March 2018.&lt;SEP&gt;The total cash flow amount for EduCorp during the accounting period.&lt;SEP&gt;The total value of the acquisition between Fabrikon and Precision Tools Inc.&lt;SEP&gt;The total value of the asset acquisition completed by Hudson Consumer Goods Co. for Greenfield Cosmetics.&lt;SEP&gt;The total value of the asset acquisition of MedTech Innovations by HealthLife Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The value of the TrendAnalytica acquisition by AccuTech Solutions Inc. was $50 million.&lt;SEP&gt;This partnership contributed to an increase in the company's net profit by $50 million.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-172d125900dc0bcb2f2f6e8c647bed84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-378748ed07de83ad7e3972e570db47df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e67632d91c7ee816e23d8224e0e65e06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37823f4768f1b122e103c53afad3b01c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4a678b6a84c2762e6b28cfe72efb9ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1f8810a724fa1483ed2f58329df5b5e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cd38eacb7e4821769dcfc4bd2eddffb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b862089f4478d18a9f621c25e0c5fe6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e3f6e287c6f25911c670ec67ee1f698&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eeaa2e4da783723d5dd539faed7d52b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b126765c2a1a1d5e39af4baef9635bc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1436b694dc38afdf4b2596a66549008&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e93a0085714fa5b062baed2fcca5006e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cc7f78ba78fbef47b769f70caf97870&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-569ff0d906c10ae60905c06ac1b2dc43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27ef22e785af8b29b73f99350c8fecd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65dd8c12a501e09197c8d83b79cebfab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb201805b67a535380cef58ba1b39de0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8f078d121c1f385db0d07f2a8fba5d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7fe5bd350cf9127c3e451699a3bf2cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21d4444cf8367fcea08fe1f13386ad32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c96445f9a1fc39affa0c0219c787367d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef8f0c36a1642ecf78e9480e727d648d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d89d6d07304989725335c5833b7cceef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5dcdee98fb35a40a6d5df48cfb39eae</data>
