<node id="RISK MANAGEMENT MEASURES">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Actions taken by the organization to identify, assess, mitigate, and manage risks.&lt;SEP&gt;EduCorp took measures to manage risks during the reporting period.&lt;SEP&gt;Elevate Retail implemented risk management measures in November 2020 to proactively manage risks and ensure stable operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Enhanced risk management measures implemented by Energen Solutions Ltd in March 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;In May 2019, StrongBuild Construction updated its risk management measures to identify new risks and implement mitigation strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;Included strategies to protect against financial losses, project delays, and reputational damage during the construction projects undertaken by Buildcorp Holdings in 2018.&lt;SEP&gt;Initiatives or actions taken by the company to manage and mitigate risks.&lt;SEP&gt;JetWing Aviation implemented risk management measures in August 2021 to improve its response to potential risks and ensure stable development.&lt;SEP&gt;Stellar Entertainment Holdings Ltd has implemented measures to manage risks effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Strategies are put in place to manage potential risks effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Strategies implemented to identify, assess, mitigate, and control potential risks that could affect the organization's objectives.&lt;SEP&gt;Strategies put in place by Acme Financial Services to mitigate risks related to governance issues.&lt;SEP&gt;The company implemented measures to identify, assess, and mitigate risks to ensure operational stability.&lt;SEP&gt;The company implemented these measures to identify and mitigate risks.&lt;SEP&gt;The company implemented various risk management measures to mitigate potential threats and uncertainties in May 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The event involved the implementation of updated risk management strategies by the company.&lt;SEP&gt;The proactive approach taken by Entertainment Enterprises Inc. in strengthening its risk management measures in October 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;The risk management measures implemented by InnovateTech Solutions aim to safeguard its operations and future prospects.&lt;SEP&gt;The updated measures reflect proactive steps taken by companies to identify and mitigate potential risks.&lt;SEP&gt;Updated measures taken by Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services in December 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;Vanguard Media Group implemented measures to manage internal and external risks, aiming for continuous operation and stable development.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0748300f32f88a4740eb7ef7cfb517ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8440ef65bcd843235214033b6db22137&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-616e42670e991c2ac8243c470d91c934&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2adee9fc3d0bd93ecfe6ec4aa0bfe19c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c431a7fe4bc601ef3e3e1bf35b7a4efa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33932faa16361e1e707b2d2c6efb3a70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-562d5dbee7bdb3cd1043414b12467feb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0b5432834bbd76f3e7b4ab9237838df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f81a0873a042e852432284ffc943889&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4133f376a9d193786338c403213110bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-554abf4656d655006b1c6f96321cf4ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33a67d86a98c46387dc267affebca479&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b353d3fc5f849d010df28587fcb285&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b77eda45ff963ad3b275398a286f3fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdb6c47bc6c218e37e6ccdda5b29bbbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c50e2e0f23f925e42b185c33f000f69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba905620b4dc9484fc4a3e905fb4a407&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f51f8d4f8b41582f6b704856b11e8b06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93deec396c94228d78f9f9db88bafc43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84c6d9a8654decbc0c8064c8d01cbe8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73adc04ec9faeb9d674508a5fc52ea0</data>
