<node id="CORPORATE GOVERNANCE REVISION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Energex Corporation revised its corporate governance policies to enhance transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;In April 2020, HealthLife Solutions revised its corporate governance policy to prioritize ethical conduct, diversity, and sustainability.&lt;SEP&gt;In January 2019, Energen Solutions Ltd underwent a significant revision of its corporate governance policy to align with industry best practices, enhance transparency and accountability, promote stakeholder engagement, encourage diversity in board composition, strengthen risk oversight mechanisms, and ensure long-term success and sustainability.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2017, SkyQuest Airlines revised its corporate governance policy to enhance transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement, emphasizing ethical practices, responsible decision-making, and financial transparency within the organization.&lt;SEP&gt;In May, MediaCorp revised its corporate governance policies to enhance transparency and accountability.&lt;SEP&gt;The company revised its corporate governance policy in June 2020 to improve transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;The corporate governance policies at Sunrise Holidays were revised in November 2019 to enhance transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of revising corporate governance policies to improve transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of updating and improving corporate governance practices at InnovateTech Solutions, aiming for transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.</data>
