  <data key="d0">GEO</data>
  <data key="d1">San Francisco is a city located in California, United States. It serves as the cultural, commercial, and financial center of Northern California.&lt;SEP&gt;San Francisco is a major city in California known for its vibrant tech industry and cultural diversity.&lt;SEP&gt;San Francisco is a major city in California, USA, known for its technology sector and innovation.&lt;SEP&gt;San Francisco is the largest city and cultural center of Northern California, located on the west coast of the United States.&lt;SEP&gt;San Francisco, CA is the location where InnovaTech Solutions is based.</data>
