<node id="ENERGEX CORPORATION">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Energex Corporation is a leading energy company established on January 1, 1990, based in Houston, Texas. It specializes in exploration, production, and distribution of oil and gas resources worldwide and is listed on the New York Stock Exchange.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a major energy provider that revised its corporate governance policies to enhance transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a major player in the energy industry that completed an acquisition.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a prominent organization in the energy sector that has shown strong commitment to corporate governance, sustainability, and social responsibility throughout 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a prominent player in the energy sector, known for its robust financial performance and strategic initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a utility company that has outlined governance improvement plans including training programs for the Board of Directors and Supervisory Board.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is a utility company that takes disciplinary actions for conflicts of interest.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an energy company that achieved significant financial performance due to exploration success and strategic investments.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an energy company that discovered major oil in the Gulf of Mexico.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization focused on delivering energy services, planning risk management strategies, and promoting sustainability in the industry.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization focused on energy-related operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization involved in the energy industry that experienced significant events in 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization specializing in renewable energy solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization that focuses on risk management and operates within the energy sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization that focuses on sustainability and social responsibility initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization that secured investment for infrastructure expansion and upgrade.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is an organization that updated its corporate governance practices to align with various laws and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Energex Corporation is known for maintaining high standards of corporate governance and ensuring timely information disclosure.</data>
