<node id="SPARKLING CLEAN HOUSEKEEPING SERVICES">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services is a professional cleaning service provider established in January 2005 in City Centre, London. Specializing in comprehensive cleaning, organizing, and maintenance services, the company has demonstrated a commitment to sustainability, social responsibility, and strong governance practices. Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services reported significant financial figures in 2019 with a return on equity of 14.5%. The organization has implemented advanced CRM systems, robust policies, procedures, and measures for compliance, and expanded its market reach through strategic partnerships. It also faced challenges due to the global pandemic in 2020 and strengthened its risk management practices. In June 2019, the company focused on improving management processes by recruiting senior executives and updating its risk management measures. The organization has consistently provided high-quality service packages targeting affluent customers and published regular financial reports for transparency with stakeholders. Its commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction is reflected in its strong shareholder equity.</data>
