<node id="WILLIAMS">
  <data key="d0">PERSON</data>
  <data key="d1">A city official who, despite being entrusted to serve with integrity and uphold legal and ethical standards, misused his office.&lt;SEP&gt;A prominent individual who holds an influential position in the municipal government.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual involved in the unauthorized collusion with contractors as indicated by recovered contracts and emails.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual who circumvented regular municipal protocols for personal and financial gain from contracts and arrangements.&lt;SEP&gt;Williams is a person who manipulated bidding processes to favor certain contractors with undisclosed financial ties.&lt;SEP&gt;Williams is an individual who manipulated zoning laws for personal benefit.&lt;SEP&gt;Williams is an individual who received substantial deposits in his bank accounts, likely related to contract winnings.&lt;SEP&gt;Williams is an organization with a strong background in technology and innovation.&lt;SEP&gt;Williams is involved in zoning law manipulation.</data>
