ther person involved in the attempted repair arrangements, interacting with Mr. R. Lee.&lt;SEP&gt;G. Torres is the owner of a local retail store who was accused of selling counterfeit goods.&lt;SEP&gt;The defendant in the case related to this legal proceeding.&lt;SEP&gt;The female defendant in the case with a birthday on November 11th, born in 1960, living at 10 Ashton Street, and working as an elementary school teacher.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual against whom the judgment was issued.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual facing sentencing for involvement in the counterfeit goods case.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual whose case was heard by the court and found guilty of a traffic accident crime.</data>
