<node id="PRESENT ILLNESS">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A condition or state that is currently affecting an individual, characterized by symptoms starting 6 months ago at home with a gradual onset, alternating periods of mild improvement and worsening. Prodromal symptoms included occasional sadness. A potential trigger for this illness might be the loss of a close friend.&lt;SEP&gt;The condition being discussed started 6 months ago at home with a gradual onset and no identifiable triggers.&lt;SEP&gt;The condition described in the medical record detailing symptoms noted immediately after birth and ongoing issues related to mouth opening and sucking.&lt;SEP&gt;The current condition being experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health condition being discussed.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health condition being experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health condition being experienced.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health condition described as onset 1 day ago at home after consuming fresh fava beans, leading to hemolysis, severe abdominal pain, fatigue, and dizziness within 24 hours post ingestion.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health condition of the patient characterized by symptoms such as high fever, dry cough, difficulty breathing, and aggravated symptoms during exertion.&lt;SEP&gt;The current health issue experienced by the patient. It began 3 months ago at home with a gradual onset and no specific prodromal symptoms identified. Possible aging-related onset is considered.&lt;SEP&gt;The current illness being experienced by the patient is characterized by gradual onset of symptoms 5 days ago, including swelling, redness behind the ear, and tenderness over the mastoid process. Swelling has progressed with increasing tenderness and occasional purulent discharge.&lt;SEP&gt;The current medical condition being described in the context.&lt;SEP&gt;The current medical condition being experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state of health experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state of illness or condition being experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state of the patient's health characterized by sudden onset blurred vision, severe headache, accompanying symptoms like eye pain and nausea, and other related issues.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state or condition being discussed.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state or condition being experienced by the patient.&lt;SEP&gt;The current state or condition of the patient's health.&lt;SEP&gt;The illness experienced by the patient after returning from a trip to Nigeria.&lt;SEP&gt;The ongoing health issue being discussed.</data>
