<node id="GENERAL HEALTH CONDITION">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">The general health condition of an individual is typically described as being in a healthy state without any significant past illnesses or chronic conditions. They usually enjoy good physical and mental well-being, have effective management of hypertension if present, and generally maintain their health through regular check-ups. This person has experienced occasional seasonal allergies but otherwise leads a life characterized by robust overall health status and minimal chronic illnesses. Their current health status is often reported as being good or excellent for their age. Despite any past medical issues such as hypertension managed with medication, the individual's overall health remains largely unimpaired, indicating no major previous health issues that have affected their well-being.</data>
