<node id="PULSE">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">PULSE is a measure of the number of heartbeats per minute (bpm), indicating cardiovascular activity. It reflects various heart rates ranging from 70 bpm to 150 bpm, depending on different conditions or measurements. The data indicates that a pulse rate of 76 bpm, measured using standard methods like a pulse oximeter, suggests a steady heartbeat without any pathological changes. However, higher readings such as 105 bpm and 110 bpm can indicate tachycardia under certain circumstances. A reading of 150 bpm may suggest an increased heart rate related to stress or exertion. The heart rate measured at 100 bpm is significantly elevated compared to the normal range, while a reading of 98 bpm suggests a healthy level for an adult. Overall, PULSE provides insights into the individual's heart rate and its variability throughout different situations.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d78a7957f61da67dfcd59aab146d3050&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee48a666f78012c5d3d1bc8a9197ad1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91de79cee694893e7909b31d0fe81e78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c7a9f95af99b59f794de118c9138134&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5172824f6269e28bb6ae341c2f6c4d35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb455f365ca081f8d11526e9a5c93a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a234d6cc704cb3799adcc31eb85c5da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5222799d7bfba1408c816526a939e5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d39efaec9bec96810ee9323f0f40db82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e03f309e9298571732b549cd7ae1d50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-349f8bebd431530c964bbe13428dafa6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b82517aceb6115b66833b4f8d1113977&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ef91345c594fb99cc0560cc10c6cfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d23944407915efd4d881ed55bdfd0e1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39d9dac6bdd47f0ba92b04b21779cdf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55dbf325604c55661148b830eeff5b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58bd966ed38f72a7a1a3b148a9ff6c74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70a919a4543aa67ce8c871937fb53ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ecb90743fae1c9ddf15b0f431848ae5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c5493bd7b9a1dd3b8744ae06dd09c5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c24e689e1ffe0c93d78faf2e1a68518d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-866f8a930b6453dc13987b3ef91516a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-961d590042206604b23fa63e325a6657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bae738e15320f2addcb046fe4b237df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f11a5e6daaf50af004c707fbd34abf4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2b258a882645dd7e5231b1bd84b822f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e760f3a1d7bb6ec5b4867f0a310494b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af866763d85cb712d130a5292d7aaf32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53062d4d7c03ed96ee30475c71e37540&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-758501a57caf1471a0236abc020af5db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c3ef585dbbfef14205d9d8ddd1649bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7f07cb078be006d0d483460a43cbefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a9cf6c8e4f4e1598931b827864beac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ecbcb19223b72e64ceb4efc9b95b398</data>
