<node id="RESPIRATION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Respiration is defined as the act or process of breathing, and in this context refers to the number of breaths taken per minute. Multiple descriptions indicate that a patient's respiration rate can vary between 16 to 24 breaths per minute, with some measurements showing rates within the normal range for adults. A respiratory rate of 18 breaths per minute is noted as being within the typical range for most patients and does not suggest any immediate respiratory issues. However, higher rates such as 22 or 24 breaths per minute may indicate shallow breathing or respiratory distress if significantly above normal values. The measured respiration rate also helps in determining the patient's overall health status.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ee48a666f78012c5d3d1bc8a9197ad1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91de79cee694893e7909b31d0fe81e78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c7a9f95af99b59f794de118c9138134&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5172824f6269e28bb6ae341c2f6c4d35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb455f365ca081f8d11526e9a5c93a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a234d6cc704cb3799adcc31eb85c5da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5222799d7bfba1408c816526a939e5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d39efaec9bec96810ee9323f0f40db82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e03f309e9298571732b549cd7ae1d50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-349f8bebd431530c964bbe13428dafa6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b82517aceb6115b66833b4f8d1113977&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ef91345c594fb99cc0560cc10c6cfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d23944407915efd4d881ed55bdfd0e1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39d9dac6bdd47f0ba92b04b21779cdf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58bd966ed38f72a7a1a3b148a9ff6c74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70a919a4543aa67ce8c871937fb53ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c5493bd7b9a1dd3b8744ae06dd09c5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c24e689e1ffe0c93d78faf2e1a68518d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-866f8a930b6453dc13987b3ef91516a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-961d590042206604b23fa63e325a6657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bae738e15320f2addcb046fe4b237df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f11a5e6daaf50af004c707fbd34abf4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2b258a882645dd7e5231b1bd84b822f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e760f3a1d7bb6ec5b4867f0a310494b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af866763d85cb712d130a5292d7aaf32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53062d4d7c03ed96ee30475c71e37540&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-758501a57caf1471a0236abc020af5db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7f07cb078be006d0d483460a43cbefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a9cf6c8e4f4e1598931b827864beac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ecbcb19223b72e64ceb4efc9b95b398</data>
