<node id="BLOOD PRESSURE">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Blood pressure is a critical measure of cardiovascular health, typically expressed in millimeters of mercury (mmHg) and recorded with two numbers: the systolic pressure being higher than the diastolic. The provided data presents various blood pressure readings for different individuals or instances, ranging from 65/40 mmHg indicating potential hypotension to 140/90 mmHg suggesting hypertension based on current standards. Some readings show stable cardiovascular function without concerns of hypertension or hypotension (e.g., a reading of 130/80 mmHg), while others indicate prehypertension risk due to elevated systolic pressure like 130/85 mmHg. Measurements taken during physical examinations consistently reflect values around 130/80 mmHg, suggesting varying levels of cardiovascular health and potential for hypertension risk in some cases.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d78a7957f61da67dfcd59aab146d3050&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee48a666f78012c5d3d1bc8a9197ad1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91de79cee694893e7909b31d0fe81e78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c7a9f95af99b59f794de118c9138134&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5172824f6269e28bb6ae341c2f6c4d35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb455f365ca081f8d11526e9a5c93a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b8904b2bc7948781e5584d7907ce799&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a234d6cc704cb3799adcc31eb85c5da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5222799d7bfba1408c816526a939e5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d39efaec9bec96810ee9323f0f40db82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e03f309e9298571732b549cd7ae1d50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-349f8bebd431530c964bbe13428dafa6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b82517aceb6115b66833b4f8d1113977&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-23b0521a3cc50967d70bb37149f6e084&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ef91345c594fb99cc0560cc10c6cfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d23944407915efd4d881ed55bdfd0e1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39d9dac6bdd47f0ba92b04b21779cdf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55dbf325604c55661148b830eeff5b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58bd966ed38f72a7a1a3b148a9ff6c74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70a919a4543aa67ce8c871937fb53ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ecb90743fae1c9ddf15b0f431848ae5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c5493bd7b9a1dd3b8744ae06dd09c5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c24e689e1ffe0c93d78faf2e1a68518d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-866f8a930b6453dc13987b3ef91516a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-961d590042206604b23fa63e325a6657&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bae738e15320f2addcb046fe4b237df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f11a5e6daaf50af004c707fbd34abf4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2b258a882645dd7e5231b1bd84b822f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c152973d0da266ffb96eaaa21a1dd9bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e760f3a1d7bb6ec5b4867f0a310494b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af866763d85cb712d130a5292d7aaf32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53062d4d7c03ed96ee30475c71e37540&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-758501a57caf1471a0236abc020af5db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c3ef585dbbfef14205d9d8ddd1649bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7f07cb078be006d0d483460a43cbefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a9cf6c8e4f4e1598931b827864beac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ecbcb19223b72e64ceb4efc9b95b398</data>
