<node id="EXTERNAL GENITALIA">
  <data key="d0">ORGAN</data>
  <data key="d1">External genitalia, also known as external reproductive organs or genitals, refer to the visible structures of the body related to sexual function and reproduction. This includes both male and female reproductive organs that are externally located on the body. The external genitalia for males include structures such as the penis and scrotum, while females have external genitalia including the vulva, which consists of the labia majora, labia minora, clitoris, and vaginal opening.

A normal inspection of these external genitalia was conducted to assess their normalcy based on age and function. The examination confirmed that the external genitalia were within normal limits for the individual's age and gender, with no abnormalities detected during the process. This included a thorough observation and assessment of both male and female external genitalia as they pertain to typical development.

No contradictions were identified in these descriptions, providing a comprehensive understanding of the external genitalia and their inspection based on age-appropriate development.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7c478a9dc4fcffd29e9d0af866dcb788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f5a7cc4481d7e5a8a75cbd38ea6c03f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0e0a9704da34cac29b4270777ab75f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d940e973757c65abfb5835ebca06f8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-426fdb1ed72ccd401a8599f4271eed36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37ccd5990d7fe8cbc76f9a5a9533c933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb455f365ca081f8d11526e9a5c93a1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd841dc7f392758b3681dd6d004ffd1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a44d343d034ad80b25ef60eb3836e2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8866dff67fd84552bd2577ca85b1ee3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-452f728b262b489a8c39838e1fd23b8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-859c12e472713ddc719ca76257b2ade0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4731b4212673d213c4c8b7faacea74c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55361f5c0d26423b49852b2a7a31df6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3feba36e0a6f08d8140050af9be9dd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f392fe7ead7d41be798eeda2e366c176&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64477ffc186b3d8f3c5869faebbf3c19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2995f536cbe35aec6a512554734543e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-deb52d98a8823e8b7150874a748d3aef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3581d6417100c6803f9a49c0780ff893&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b59f304ada4f6fddff18261a513d556c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f5ce64d2a3a688f86165b0724422c77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f0adc492ff59d40ba8de3d1b08909c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc101c6e3036837cff044a261554d391&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f19d10898e456bacb3f8ad20e5d3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84459077f8a85743c39777e804ed54b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce34a4cb3bbfaa9cf9e8a30cf41be706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73459b5b43c0a8cd80ceef72dba5e00a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-476b66a97b6e2c3e166550fcf3ff5621&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5547ecd249cfe0d6f9118ac04260775&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dee99d110be8af9ee1a4218821ca66e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5fdd2cc7df8204e78df4d5dcb0d72c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea14ddac9f9f01287f5a0962ce3503d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f46de81e5607e987607ace480022c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f4dd25a9395cb6e9866994eeee1638</data>
