<node id="SPINE">
  <data key="d0">ORGAN</data>
  <data key="d1">The spine, also known as the backbone, is a column of bones (vertebrae) that runs from the skull to the tailbone, providing support for the body and protecting the spinal cord. It is a complex structure in the human body that serves as the central support for the body, connecting the brain and spinal cord with the rest of the body. The spine's normal alignment and curvature suggest an absence of spinal abnormalities or deformities. In this specific context, no deformities or tenderness were observed in the patient's spine during examination, indicating a healthy condition without local discomfort or injury.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7c478a9dc4fcffd29e9d0af866dcb788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f5a7cc4481d7e5a8a75cbd38ea6c03f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0e0a9704da34cac29b4270777ab75f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d940e973757c65abfb5835ebca06f8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-426fdb1ed72ccd401a8599f4271eed36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37ccd5990d7fe8cbc76f9a5a9533c933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd841dc7f392758b3681dd6d004ffd1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4634a4b54e852881a10381d7eb0ad48f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a44d343d034ad80b25ef60eb3836e2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8866dff67fd84552bd2577ca85b1ee3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-312b459cafc01b1ce8d35628d148d758&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-452f728b262b489a8c39838e1fd23b8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-859c12e472713ddc719ca76257b2ade0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4731b4212673d213c4c8b7faacea74c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55361f5c0d26423b49852b2a7a31df6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3feba36e0a6f08d8140050af9be9dd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f392fe7ead7d41be798eeda2e366c176&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64477ffc186b3d8f3c5869faebbf3c19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2995f536cbe35aec6a512554734543e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-deb52d98a8823e8b7150874a748d3aef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60a32ea6d511a15b5ebfe4dffa08322a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-149908a8c44d7a34c2949c659110618d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625541468d2ae23923cded39f6384f95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3581d6417100c6803f9a49c0780ff893&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b59f304ada4f6fddff18261a513d556c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f0adc492ff59d40ba8de3d1b08909c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f9253512418c7574d1462077c913e0a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc101c6e3036837cff044a261554d391&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f19d10898e456bacb3f8ad20e5d3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84459077f8a85743c39777e804ed54b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce34a4cb3bbfaa9cf9e8a30cf41be706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-139006d2a22f7b5f524e60fc7e6c1955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73459b5b43c0a8cd80ceef72dba5e00a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91e4a396013569ef5e4ac7f8a5d9e9f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4eee628a7f138c48a83ace42abf791de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-476b66a97b6e2c3e166550fcf3ff5621&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5547ecd249cfe0d6f9118ac04260775&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dee99d110be8af9ee1a4218821ca66e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69a00f95b43712991f92b4a11bf903e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9944777c320c130ae7aef53725a3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea14ddac9f9f01287f5a0962ce3503d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7d892f9926e9ee82fae6a705fa2d296&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f46de81e5607e987607ace480022c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f4dd25a9395cb6e9866994eeee1638</data>
