<node id="LIMBS">
  <data key="d0">ORGAN</data>
  <data key="d1">The limbs are a set of appendages used for movement, including arms and legs, which are essential parts of the human body's musculoskeletal system responsible for locomotion and interaction with the environment. A comprehensive examination of the limbs revealed no deformities or abnormalities, full range of motion, and absence of edema (swelling). No cyanosis was observed, indicating normal muscle strength and tone. The assessment also noted that there were no signs of clubbing, deformities, edema, or restrictions in movement. Overall, the limbs are functioning without any problems as per the medical review. However, a tremor was observed in the right hand, accompanied by mild rigidity in limbs and bradykinesia with reduced dexterity.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7c478a9dc4fcffd29e9d0af866dcb788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0e0a9704da34cac29b4270777ab75f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d940e973757c65abfb5835ebca06f8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-426fdb1ed72ccd401a8599f4271eed36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37ccd5990d7fe8cbc76f9a5a9533c933&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd841dc7f392758b3681dd6d004ffd1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4634a4b54e852881a10381d7eb0ad48f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8866dff67fd84552bd2577ca85b1ee3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-452f728b262b489a8c39838e1fd23b8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-859c12e472713ddc719ca76257b2ade0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4731b4212673d213c4c8b7faacea74c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3feba36e0a6f08d8140050af9be9dd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f392fe7ead7d41be798eeda2e366c176&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64477ffc186b3d8f3c5869faebbf3c19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2995f536cbe35aec6a512554734543e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-deb52d98a8823e8b7150874a748d3aef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-149908a8c44d7a34c2949c659110618d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625541468d2ae23923cded39f6384f95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3581d6417100c6803f9a49c0780ff893&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b59f304ada4f6fddff18261a513d556c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f0adc492ff59d40ba8de3d1b08909c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f9253512418c7574d1462077c913e0a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc101c6e3036837cff044a261554d391&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52f19d10898e456bacb3f8ad20e5d3c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce34a4cb3bbfaa9cf9e8a30cf41be706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73459b5b43c0a8cd80ceef72dba5e00a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91e4a396013569ef5e4ac7f8a5d9e9f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4eee628a7f138c48a83ace42abf791de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-476b66a97b6e2c3e166550fcf3ff5621&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5547ecd249cfe0d6f9118ac04260775&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dee99d110be8af9ee1a4218821ca66e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9944777c320c130ae7aef53725a3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5fdd2cc7df8204e78df4d5dcb0d72c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea14ddac9f9f01287f5a0962ce3503d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7d892f9926e9ee82fae6a705fa2d296&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f46de81e5607e987607ace480022c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f4dd25a9395cb6e9866994eeee1638</data>
