<node id="NERVOUS SYSTEM">
  <data key="d0">ORGAN</data>
  <data key="d1">The nervous system is a complex network that controls various functions in the body, including movement, sensation, and cognition. It includes components such as cranial nerves, motor functions, sensory functions, and cognitive abilities. In this context, all descriptions indicate an alert and oriented state with intact cranial nerves II-XII and no focal neurological deficits detected during examination. Reflexes were found to be brisk or normal, and patients exhibited normal motor strength and sensation across all extremities. The patient did not present any signs of impaired rapid alternating movements or hypertonicity (increased muscle tone). No muscular weaknesses or limited mouth opening were noted. Overall, the nervous system functions properly without any reported deficits or issues, ensuring the individual remains alert, oriented to person, place, and time, with normal reflexes intact.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-86639a8894efa4336bef2f5598aff2f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c478a9dc4fcffd29e9d0af866dcb788&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0e0a9704da34cac29b4270777ab75f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d940e973757c65abfb5835ebca06f8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-426fdb1ed72ccd401a8599f4271eed36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd841dc7f392758b3681dd6d004ffd1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-452f728b262b489a8c39838e1fd23b8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-859c12e472713ddc719ca76257b2ade0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4731b4212673d213c4c8b7faacea74c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3feba36e0a6f08d8140050af9be9dd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f392fe7ead7d41be798eeda2e366c176&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64477ffc186b3d8f3c5869faebbf3c19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-deb52d98a8823e8b7150874a748d3aef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-149908a8c44d7a34c2949c659110618d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625541468d2ae23923cded39f6384f95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3581d6417100c6803f9a49c0780ff893&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b59f304ada4f6fddff18261a513d556c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f0adc492ff59d40ba8de3d1b08909c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f9253512418c7574d1462077c913e0a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc101c6e3036837cff044a261554d391&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84459077f8a85743c39777e804ed54b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce34a4cb3bbfaa9cf9e8a30cf41be706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73459b5b43c0a8cd80ceef72dba5e00a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91e4a396013569ef5e4ac7f8a5d9e9f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4eee628a7f138c48a83ace42abf791de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-476b66a97b6e2c3e166550fcf3ff5621&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5547ecd249cfe0d6f9118ac04260775&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dee99d110be8af9ee1a4218821ca66e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9944777c320c130ae7aef53725a3d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5fdd2cc7df8204e78df4d5dcb0d72c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea14ddac9f9f01287f5a0962ce3503d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f4dd25a9395cb6e9866994eeee1638</data>
