<node id="IMMUNOLOGY">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Immunology is the branch of medicine that focuses on understanding how the immune system works to protect the body from infections and diseases. It encompasses various components such as lymph nodes, antibodies, and immune cells like T-cells and B-cells.</data>
