</node>
<node id="NEUROPSYCHIATRY">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Neuropsychiatry is a medical specialty at the intersection of neurology and psychiatry. It focuses on how brain disorders affect behavior and mental health, including cognitive functions, emotional regulation, and social interactions.</data>
