<edge source="DIVIDEND DISTRIBUTION" target="SHAREHOLDER EQUITY">
  <data key="d4">68.0</data>
  <data key="d5">Distribution of dividends also contributed to the increase in shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividend distribution decreases the shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividend distribution impacts the level of shareholder equity by distributing profits to shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividends distributed reduce the balance of shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividends reduce shareholder equity as they represent part of the earnings being paid out to shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividends reduce the overall value of shareholder equity when distributed.&lt;SEP&gt;Shareholder equity is affected by the amount distributed as dividends.&lt;SEP&gt;The dividend distribution is part of the shareholder equity after profits are allocated.</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-b28a3f8a89e0fcae38abdedbe544659a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86068dde10a230e2e4323fb0cac9f2a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc3208201d6561b422fb226e4ff25a4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fbeecff4ad670e578dbf231af003adee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5d3ac39d226934014646efa4174b9a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6585389e40eae15ca4b23b55b02e27e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1595bc63912d3131553c638d8afb11d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6d3080d8490190ea1e4344239d03f12</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
